forecast function!

fcst.Rd

forecast function!

fcst(type, ...)

Arguments

type

either arma, aruma, sigplusnoise, or other tswge model. No quotes
...

the normal inputs to tswge

Value

a forecast

Examples

fcst(arma, LakeHuron, phi = 0.2)
